<h1>Library FAQ</h1>
<p>Here are some frequently asked questions and answers about our online libraray. If you have any other questions, please contact us.</p>
<h2>Q: How can I access to my management site?</h2>
<p>A: You can register to our management site then loged in to our management sector and enjoy!</p>
<h2>Q: How can I describe my problem and contact to the Admin?</h2>
<p>A: When you log into your mamangement account you will see that there will be a help and support option where admin and you both manage contact with each other. </p>     
<h2>Q: How can I purchased books from your website?</h2>
<p>A: You can purchased books from our website by browsing our catalog, adding the books you want to your cart, and checking out with your preferred payment method. You will need to create an account or log in to your existing account to complete your order.</p>
<h2>Q: What are the shipping options and costs?</h2>
<p>A: We offer free standard shipping for orders over 500 tk. For orders under 500 tk, we charge a flat rate of 40 tk for standard shipping. We also offer expedited shipping for an additional fee, depending on the destination and weight of the order. You can see the shipping options and costs at checkout before placing your order.</p>
<h2>Q: How can I track my status and delivery?</h2>
<p>A: You can track your status and delivery by logging in to your account and clicking on "My Orders". You will see the order number, date, status, and tracking number for each order. You can also click on the tracking number to see the delivery details on the carrier's website.</p>
<h2>Q: What is your return and refund policy?</h2>
<p>A: We want you to be happy with your purchase. If you are not satisfied with your order, you can return it within 30 days of delivery for a full refund or exchange. The books must be in their original condition and packaging. You will need to contact us to request a return authorization and a prepaid shipping label. Once we receive and inspect your return, we will process your refund or exchange within 10 business days.</p>
<h2>Q: How can I contact you for more information or assistance?</h2>
<p>A: You can contact us by email, phone, or chat. Our email address is support@onlinelibrary.com. Our phone number is 1-800-Libraray-ONLINE. Our chat service is available from 9 am to 5 pm EST, Monday to Friday. We are happy to help you with any questions or issues you may have.</p>
